data.description:
Delightful and inviting house featuring three bedrooms and two baths. 
You will be captivated by its well-maintained exterior, and a neatly paved pathway leading to the entrance. Stepping inside, you are greeted by an open floor plan, providing an ideal setting for entertaining.
The primary bedroom boasts generous space. Offering a private en-suite bathroom with a walk-in shower, a bathtub and double sinks. The two additional bedrooms are equally comfortable and spacious, providing plenty of room for children, guests, or a home office.
Outside offers an ample backyard with a gazebo! Whether you envision hosting summer barbecues or simply enjoying quiet moments of tranquility, the possibilities are endless in this beautiful outdoor space. Additional features include a separate laundry area, and a two-car garage for parking convenience plus a driveway plus parking on the side of the house!!!
Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this charming house your dream home.
